fields.name: Wireless Bluetooth Headphones
fields.description: Premium wireless headphones with active noise cancellation, 30-hour battery life, and comfortable over-ear design. Features include touch controls, voice assistant support, and high-fidelity audio drivers for an immersive listening experience.

fields.name: Smartphone Stand with Wireless Charger
fields.description: Elegant aluminum smartphone stand with built-in 15W fast wireless charging. Compatible with all Qi-enabled devices. Adjustable viewing angle perfect for video calls and desk organization.

fields.name: Mechanical Keyboard RGB
fields.description: Full-size mechanical keyboard with customizable RGB backlighting. Features Cherry MX Blue switches for tactile feedback, dedicated media controls, and USB passthrough. Built with an aluminum frame for durability.

fields.name: 4K Webcam with Ring Light
fields.description: Ultra HD 4K webcam with built-in adjustable ring light for perfect lighting in any environment. Auto-focus, noise-canceling microphone, and privacy cover included. Ideal for streaming and video conferencing.

fields.name: Classic Denim Jacket
fields.description: Timeless medium-wash denim jacket with button closure. Features chest pockets, adjustable waist tabs, and premium 100% cotton construction. A versatile wardrobe essential that pairs with everything.

fields.name: Cotton Crew Neck T-Shirt Pack
fields.description: Pack of 5 premium cotton crew neck t-shirts in assorted colors (black, white, gray, navy, olive). Pre-shrunk fabric, tagless design for comfort, and reinforced seams for durability.

fields.name: Running Sneakers
fields.description: Lightweight running shoes with responsive foam cushioning and breathable mesh upper. Features a durable rubber outsole for excellent traction and reflective details for visibility during evening runs.

fields.name: The Art of Programming
fields.description: A comprehensive guide to software development principles and best practices. Covers clean code, design patterns, testing strategies, and career advice for developers at all levels. 500+ pages with practical examples.

fields.name: Mystery Novel Collection
fields.description: Box set of 6 bestselling mystery novels featuring detective Sarah Chen. Award-winning series that will keep you guessing until the final page. Perfect for mystery lovers and book club discussions.

fields.name: Modern Minimalist Desk Lamp
fields.description: Sleek LED desk lamp with adjustable brightness levels and color temperature settings. Features a USB charging port, touch controls, and a flexible gooseneck design. Energy-efficient and stylish.

fields.name: Indoor Plant Starter Kit
fields.description: Complete kit for growing indoor plants including 3 ceramic pots with drainage, premium potting soil, plant food, and seeds for herbs and succulents. Perfect for beginners and urban gardeners.

fields.name: Cozy Throw Blanket
fields.description: Ultra-soft microfiber throw blanket measuring 50x60 inches. Machine washable, fade-resistant, and perfect for movie nights on the couch. Available in this warm gray color.

fields.name: Yoga Mat Premium
fields.description: Extra thick (6mm) yoga mat with alignment lines and non-slip surface on both sides. Made from eco-friendly TPE material, includes carrying strap. Perfect for yoga, pilates, and floor exercises.

fields.name: Resistance Bands Set
fields.description: Set of 5 resistance bands with different tension levels (5-50 lbs). Includes door anchor, handles, and ankle straps. Comes with exercise guide and carrying bag. Great for home workouts.

fields.name: Insulated Water Bottle
fields.description: 32oz double-wall vacuum insulated stainless steel water bottle. Keeps drinks cold for 24 hours or hot for 12 hours. Leak-proof lid with built-in straw. BPA-free and sweat-proof exterior.
